{"word":"G1718 - ἐμφανίζω - emphanízō - em-fan-id'-zo - Appear","slug":"G1718","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐμφανίζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>emphanízō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>em-fan-id'-zo"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Appear"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B5;&#x0313;&#x03BC;&#x03C6;&#x03B1;&#x03BD;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03B6;&#x03C9; - emphanizo&#x0304;</b> - <i>em-fan-id'-zo</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G1717\">G1717</a>; to <i>exhibit</i> (in person) or <i>disclose</i> (by words): - appear, declare (plainly), inform, (will) manifest, shew, signify."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2014\">G2014</a>, <a href=\"#/G2015\">G2015</a>, <a href=\"#/G2016\">G2016</a>, <a href=\"#/G5316\">G5316</a>, <a href=\"#/G5318\">G5318</a>, <a href=\"#/G5319\">G5319</a>, <a href=\"#/G5320\">G5320</a>, <a href=\"#/G5321\">G5321</a>, <a href=\"#/G5322\">G5322</a>, <a href=\"#/G5324\">G5324</a>, <a href=\"#/G5325\">G5325</a>, <a href=\"#/G5326\">G5326</a>"}]}